{
  "page_title": "会话名称搜索",
  "apis": [
    {
      "group_title": "会话名称搜索",
      "api_name": "search_chat",
      "method": "SDK调用",
      "api_url": "",
      "description": "可调用该接口对企业的群会话名称进行搜索",
      "query_params": [
        {
          "name": "query_word",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "搜索的文本，要求大于等于2个UTF8字符"
        },
        {
          "name": "limit",
          "type": "uint32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "用于分页查询，每次请求返回的数据上限。最大为100，不填默认为50"
        },
        {
          "name": "cursor",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "用于分页查询的游标，字符串类型，由上一次调用返回，首次调用可不填"
        }
      ],
      "body_params": [],
      "response_params": [
        {
          "name": "errcode",
          "type": "int32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "错误码"
        },
        {
          "name": "errmsg",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "错误码说明"
        },
        {
          "name": "has_more",
          "type": "uint32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "是否还有更多数据未获取，不填默认为0 0: 否 1: 是"
        },
        {
          "name": "next_cursor",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "下一次请求的cursor值"
        },
        {
          "name": "chat_list",
          "type": "object[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "搜索结果的群列表"
        },
        {
          "name": "chat_list[].chatid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "群聊会话id"
        }
      ],
      "request_examples": [
        {
          "title": "请求包体示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n\t\"query_word\": \"VIP\",\n\t\"limit\": 50,\n\t\"cursor\": \"CURSOR\"\n}"
        }
      ],
      "response_examples": [
        {
          "title": "返回结果示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n\t\"errcode\": 0,\n\t\"errmsg\": \"ok\",\n\t\"has_more\": 1,\n\t\"next_cursor\": \"CURSOR\",\n\t\"chat_list\":[\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t\"chatid\": \"CHATID1\"\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t\"chatid\": \"CHATID2\"\n\t\t}\n\t]\n}"
        }
      ],
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "权限说明",
          "content": "> 对于搜索会话名称，**仅支持有命名的群聊**，对于单聊和未命名的群聊不支持搜索\n> 搜索会话名称时，基于当前最新的会话名称搜索\n\n| 应用类型 | 权限要求 |\n| --- | --- |\n| 自建应用 | 需具备「数据与智能专区权限」 |\n| 代开发应用 | 需具备「数据与智能专区权限」 |\n| 第三方应用 | 需具备「数据与智能专区权限」 |"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}